author: Reuters Editorial
title: Germania, disoccupati febbraio in calo di 22.000, tasso stabile a 5,4% Macroeconomia
text: BERLIN, Feb 28 (Reuters) - Germany's Federal Labour Office reported the following economic indicator on Wednesday : GERMAN UNEMPLOYMENT FEB 18 JAN 18 FEB 17 Change (adj) -22,000 -25,000 -13,000 Number (adj) 2.393 mln 2.415 mln 2.593 mln Rate (adj) 5.4 pct 5.4 pct 5.9 pct Change (unadj) -24,375 185,350 -15,292 Number (unadj) 2.546 mln 2.570 mln 2.762 mln Rate (unadj) 5.7 pct 5.8 pct 6.3 pct
